flowchart LR
    A[Layer output error\nE = trace of H * delta_W^2] --> B[Choose weight\nwith min saliency]
    B --> C[Set weight to zero\n/ quantize it]
    C --> D[Update remaining\nweights via H^-1]
    D --> E{More weights?}
    E -->|yes| B
    E -->|no| F[Compressed layer\n+ error compensation]
